      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver holds ISO 9001 certification; version-controlled solver release with regression test suite passing at ≥ 95% for hemolysis-relevant test cases.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2 employed under ISO 9001-certified QMS. Solver release notes confirm regression suite pass rate of 97.3% for viscous flow and scalar transport modules relevant to hemolysis prediction. Source code version pinned in simulation records."
