    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 5. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD predictions within 15% of FDA benchmark experimental data across all five operating points. UQ campaign confirms RH < 1 acceptance criterion holds at 95th percentile of geometric tolerance and viscosity parameter space. Discretization error bounded at GCI = 1.3%. Overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory decision for this Class II CPB device at Medium assurance level.",
